A medley of tropical flavours!🇯🇲🌴🏝️💥 @tsjamaicanflavours 🇯🇲
Rating: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ 5 star
Review: @tsjamaicanflavours in Charlottetown, PEI, embarks you on a tantalizing journey to Jamaica through its vibrant flavors and lively atmosphere🪩🎇The menu: a delightful fusion of Jamaican authenticity, boasting the signature smoky and savory Jerk Chicken 🍗 at the top of the list! Combined with the rhythmic reggae tunes and friendly island hospitality, @tsjamaicanflavours creates an unforgettable dining and cultural experience that transports your taste buds and spirit to the Caribbean, right in the heart of 📍downtown Charlottetown, PEI. 
#discovercharlottetown #downtowncharlottetown #pei #welcomepei

Crispy Skin Salmon Chickpea Salad 🍣 🥗 @saltandsolpei 
Rating: ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️
Review: This salmon and chickpea salad was absolutely delicious! The salmon was perfectly cooked, tender, and flavourful, while the salad was delightfully crunchy. The combination of fresh ingredients made for a delightful and satisfying meal. Highly recommended!
